# ASP.NET MVC Products

A full-stack ASP.NET Core 8 application featuring a clean Products API, MVC Razor UI frontend, MySQL database, and TailwindCSS styling.  
The project demonstrates a modern, lightweight product management dashboard using EF Core, REST API, and client-side fetch rendering.

---

## ðŸš€ Features

- ASP.NET Core 8 MVC Architecture
- REST API for Products (`/api/products`)
- MySQL database using Entity Framework Core
- Migrations enabled (`dotnet ef`)
- TailwindCSS (via CDN) for fast UI styling
- Razor Views (server-rendered) with client-side fetch
- Full CRUD structure (GET / POST implemented, ready for PUT / DELETE)
- Clean separation of MVC UI and API controllers

---

## ðŸ“¦ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** ASP.NET Core 8  
- **Database:** MySQL  
- **ORM:** Entity Framework Core  
- **Frontend:** Razor Views + TailwindCSS  
- **Client-side:** JavaScript Fetch API  
- **Architecture:** MVC + API (dual-controller system)

